### 1. Login ok

POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "12345678",
  "username": "NguyenCoderVN"
}


### 2. Login fails

POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "123456789",
  "username": "NguyenCoderVN"
}


### 1. Logout

POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/logout HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{}
